Chong-kau3-tek e5 ji5-tong5 kau3-iok8 e5 toa7 ki-koan, pi2 Chu2-jit8-oh8 a2-si7 i2-goa7, siong7 u7 lat8 si7 chai7-ti7 ka-teng5. Siat-su2 na7 bo5 ka-teng5 e5 pang-chan7, chiu7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 kau3-iok8 chha-put-to long2 pinn3 bo5 hau7. Tui3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 ji5-tong5 sou2 si-heng5 kau3-iok8, chit8-le2-pai3 ku2 chi2-u7 1 tiam2-cheng, chong2-si7 ti7 ka-teng5 kau3-iok8 ji5-tong5, hit e5 si5-kan si7 bo5-han7. Sou2-i2 ji5-tong5 kau3-iok8 e5 toa7 pou7-hun7 long2 si7 ti7 ka-teng5 si-heng5. Thiann kong2 mui2-ni5 u7 400 ban7 e5 ang5-enn-a2 chhut-si3 lai5 se3-kan, chong2-si7 chiah e5 enn-a2 sek bo5 sio-siang7, ia7 bo5 penn5 toa7-han3, m7-ku2 na7 bo5 siu7 lau7-bo2 e5 po2-hou7 chiu7 be7 tit thang ka-ti7 seng-chun5, chit e5 su7 long2 sio-siang7.
Bat u7 chit8 e5 lang5 kio3 cho3 He2-a3 kong2, “A-tong e5 lok8-hng5 si7 ti7 ka-teng5, chong2-si7 chai7-ti7 lan2 ka-teng5 chiu7-si7 lok8-hng5”, chhin-chhiunn7 Bi2-kok e5 gin2-na2 siong5-siong5 ai3 chhiunn3 “bo5 pi2 ka-teng5 khah ho2 e5 sou2-chai7” e5 khoan2, chai7-ti7 ji5-tong5 bo5 pi2 ka-teng5 khah iau3-kin2 e5 sou2-chai7, ia7 bo5 khah hoann-hi2 e5 sou2-chai7. Lang5 e5 ang5-enn-a2 pi2 cheng-senn e5 kiann2 toa7 be7 hiah kin2 chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3 ai3 beh hou7 ang5-enn-a2 ti7 lau7-bo2 e5 sin-pinn khah ku2.
Na2 chhin-chhiunn7 niau-a2-kiann2 a2-si7 kau2-a2-kiann2 e7 liam5-pinn toa7, chiu7 m7-bian2 hou7 pe7-bo2 hoan5-lo2, ia7 chin chio2 ma5-hoan5, chong2-si7 su7-sit8 pe7-bo2 teh iunn2-chhi7 kiann2-ji5 tioh8 keng-koe3 10 ni5, 15 ni5 hiah tng5 e5 ni5 goeh8 e5 tiong-kan, me5-jit8 bo5 pang3-sang chin7-sim teh iong2-iok8. An2-ni teh kau3-iok8 ji5-tong5, choe3 iau3-kin2 m7-si7 eng7 gian5-gu2 teh ka3-si7, si7 eng7 heng5-ui5 teh ka7 kam2-hoa3. Ka-teng5 choe3 toa7 e5 bok8-tek si7 chai7-ti7 cho7-chiu7 jin5-keh, sou2-i2 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 ka-teng5 e7 thang kong2 si7 cho7-chiu7 chhin-chhiunn7 Ki-tok e5 jin5-keh e5 sou2-chai7. A-to2-kin2 chit e5 lang5 kong2, “He7 ji5-tong5 ti7 ka-teng5 e5 li2-iu5, chiu7-si7 in-ui7 beh hou7 i ng3 thinn-nih hoat-tat8.”
Hian7-chai7 Jit8-pun2 e5 si7-toa7-lang5 chin toa7 chho3-gou7 e5 sou2-chai7 si7 siunn7 kong2 ka3 ji5-tong5 e5 sou2-chai7 chi2-u7 si7 hak8-hau7, ia7 ka-teng5 long2 bo5 koan-he7 e5 khoan2. Sou2-i2 tui3 sang3 ji5-tong5 khi3 hak8-hau7 e5 su7 put-chi2 u7 teh lou2-lek8, m7-ku2 tui3 ti7 ka-teng5 teh si-heng5 kau3-iok8 long2 bo5 teh chin7-lat8, kin-a2-jit8 teh chiong5-su7 ti7 phou2-thong kau3-iok8 e5 lang5 choe3 khou2-sim e5 tiam2, chiu7-si7 ai3 beh hou7 hak8-hau7 kap ka-teng5 khoann3 an2-choann2 thang sann lian5-lok8. It-poann e5 pe7-bo2 bo5 chin7-lat8 ti7 ka-teng5 e5 kau3-iok8 e5 li2-iu5, chiu7-si7 in siunn7 kong2 kau3-iok8 si7 chi2-u7 oh8 na7-tiann7, bo5 teh siunn7 kong2 si7 ka7 in thoan3-lian7, cho7-chiu7 jin5-but8.
In siunn7 kong2 chi2-u7 ti7 hak8-hau7 oh8 thak8 kap sia2, chiu7 e7 cho7-chiu7 ho2 e5 jin5-but8. Ji5-tong5 ti7 hak8-hau7 sou2 oh8 e5, pe7-bo2 tioh8 hou7 i ti7 ka-teng5 lai5 piau2-ian2 khoann3-mai7. Phi3-ju7 na7 ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 u7 hak8-sip8 tui3 Siong7-te3 ki5-to2, ti7 ka-teng5 na7 bo5 hou7 i ki5-to2, koh pe7-bo2 ka-ki7 na7 bo5 ki5-to2, sui-jian5 ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 u7 sou2 ka3 e5, ia7 long2 bo5 lou7-eng7. Khoann3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 cho3 gin2-na2 thit-tho5 e5 sou2-chai7, a2-si7 siunn7 kong2 gin2-na2 ti7 chhu3-nih kiam2-chha2 sou2-i2 ka7 sang3 khi3 Chu2-jit8-oh8, chit-khoan2 e5 siunn7-hoat chin m7-tioh8. Sui-jian5 si7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 pe7-bo2, iau2-ku2 m7-chai ji5-tong5 e5 chong-kau3 kau3-iok8 sou2-i2 sang3 gin2-na2 khi3 phou2-thong e5 hak8-hau7 chin giam5-keh, m7-ku2 sang3 khi3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 bo5 siunn7 kau3 hiah iau3-kin2.
